Basicly, i just want to delete the spawn kill of this map and i don't like how is mapped :/ (Wall in wall, no decoration, leak etc ..) I know i'm not the "better mapper" but i think i make a good work. So, if it's possible, can you vote this map ? I want a good vision of what i make/ remake. For this map, i was based of the original map and i built the map from a dead point. I use exactly the same distance (Unit's) of the orignal map.
